{"tid":1537541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跳完閘慳左嘅錢請拎曬去捐比星火","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T00:55:43.000Z","uid":17358,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"028908210a933df07169f16cafbca726acd4d693","tid":1537541,"uid":17358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"夢見好多朋友都係為跳閘而跳閘，慳左嘅錢就拎曬去吃喝玩樂，雖然拎去吃喝玩樂都無咩問題，但係我地慳左嘅錢其實可以有更大嘅用處。試想假如有20000人願意跳閘，佢地一個月嘅交通費100-1000不等，捐哂比星火每個月就多幾百萬，所以希望大家，跳左閘慳左嘅錢，拎哂去捐！<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔支持亦唔鼓勵大家跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe04defb1bee716411c5751b83802cac245894eb","tid":1537541,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong